Name: UCSB
Description: A great university located along the California coast!

Name: Yosemite National Park
Description: A beautiful national park where people go to hike, camp, and see wildlife. Some hikes include the Mist Trail and Glacier Point.

Name: La Jolla Cove
Description: A beach in San Diego where there are many seals and sea lions relaxing on the rocks.

Name: Julian
Description: A small town near San Diego where I went as a child to pick apples in the fall. It's also home to the best caramel apple pie.

Name: La Paloma Theater
Description: A very old movie theater in Encintas where they show the Rocky Horror Picture Show every Friday night at midnight, which I like to attend when I can.

Name: Santa Cruz Island
Description: One of the Northern Channel Islands located off the coast of Santa Barbara. It has many beautiful sea caves that can be explored by kayaks.
